{"tid":1370153,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"純推介音樂，為大家打打氣。","createTime":"2019-07-27T01:56:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T02:12:26.000Z","uid":287033,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b35e2f76d7493b4e685f109aa7f227a6dd6efe7","tid":1370153,"uid":287033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:56:36.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/wgHnMtfo_YY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FwgHnMtfo_YY&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=efabbf34\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/wgHnMtfo_YY</a><br />\n<br />\nKolor - 天地會<br />\n<br />\n埋葬昨天理想　投身今天戰場　錯愛錢幣肖像<br />\n城市快將要死　如果這都算正常　你我結這壞賬<br />\n<br />\n未麻木的　終於會脫離　制度壓迫　一朝過期<br />\n復明現光　青天破八旗　欲蓋是獸皮　人性是契機<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/H6cjQRI6iYw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FH6cjQRI6iYw&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=96c75ca5\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/H6cjQRI6iYw</a><br />\n<br />\nKolor - 愚公<br />\n<br />\n無欲則剛攻不破　短短一生中<br />\n轉變多　山高川急不需怯懦 <br />\n頑石一般的一個　無我里有自我"},{"pid":"5334fdc4e646aee6b2251f0d72d2f9f42570c321","tid":1370153,"uid":287033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T01:59:02.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/IwhevWYS0ZM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FIwhevWYS0ZM&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=d7d75871\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/IwhevWYS0ZM</a><br />\n<br />\nKolor - 生於憂患<br />\n<br />\n承受過安定　餵飽過繁榮<br />\n我信我　不信命　不想至死徒然贈慶是<br />\n沒有傷損　怎發育健全<br />\n從未傷風　怎懂得取暖<br />\n迷惘　是覺醒的開端　心苦過哪怕酸<br />\n若怕辛酸　生我在樂園<br />\n沈睡蘇醒　豬圈中兜轉<br />\n痲痹　是半死的開端　只知道吃喝穿"},{"pid":"915b0faeb4e817580ed36dcf21665de67667fee9","tid":1370153,"uid":287033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:02:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/gdqNbVAPp2g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FgdqNbVAPp2g&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=508d9201\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/gdqNbVAPp2g</a><br />\n<br />\nSadJay - 終章<br />\n<br />\n從來遇再強未怯場 仍然未怕率先重傷<br />\n讓我改寫走向 從求生到踏上終點一仗<br />\n尋求答案 尋求所嚮往"},{"pid":"ba82357907ab41619ba225fb475a6c4b9bdd2297","tid":1370153,"uid":157470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:02:49.000Z","msg":"KOLOR<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f0c15233165bdd6d1441ade7a5ac1ab8ce3ad46","tid":1370153,"uid":287033,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T02:12:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/TIpNx6Lg6ow\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FTIpNx6Lg6ow&d=P86Nric8SGsb572WK9RGdwexVh8qxZHot2w31qr30Zg%3D&h=4884c8f8\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/TIpNx6Lg6ow</a><br />\n<br />\nYellow - 理想再見<br />\n<br />\n學會話 離開也是智慧<br />\n但以後 誰肯歇力捍衛"}]}